{"tid":747597,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[上年錯過左的巴打 今年好醒啦]少女賣書唔找錢　𠱁加$300有「售後服務」","createTime":"2018-07-18T13:24:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-22T04:21:46.000Z","uid":54373,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"9cbaf0c3e488822d2c5609d2d1f7fdc1cd8f6629","tid":747597,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T13:24:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">今年記得至少渣2下先好幫襯<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】暑假接近尾聲，不少學生都趕買下學年的教科書，但卻有學生哥在葵涌廣場遇到不良書店，除被職員搶書單硬劏外，書店更出動短裙少女拉客，有賣書美少女竟聲稱有「售後服務」，藉詞不找續數百元餘款。另外由於現場售賣二手書競爭大，本周一有兩批人疑因爭生意爭執，其間有人揚言：「信唔信我打你！」警方接報到場以涉嫌刑事恐嚇及遊蕩罪拘捕4男6女（14至31歲），案件交葵青警區反黑組接手調查。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20170817/large/17la6p41.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170817%2Flarge%2F17la6p41.jpg&h=58b25041&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n警方周一在葵涌廣場其中一間涉事書店旁截停一批青年助查。<br />\n<br />\n葵廣二手書店賣爛書<br />\n<br />\n葵青區議員吳劍昇指，近日接獲多名市民投訴，指有人在葵涌廣場兜售二手教科書，目標是初中學生，手法是搶去對方書單帶去書店，並聲稱以低至三折賣書，到達書店後店員迅速將書入袋，曾有人遭索價1,700元，付款後回家發現全是舊版書或殘破不堪，無法使用。<br />\n<br />\n吳更發現稱有不良書店出動短裙少女拉客，曾有青少年指付款後少女職員拒絕找回數百元，並稱餘款可作「售後服務」之用，但未有透露甚麼是售後服務，最終該男生追回餘款未有理會。吳關注所謂售後服務可能涉及非法勾當，希望警方正視。<br />\n<br />\n消息指，近日有青年在葵涌廣場就賣二手書生意爭執，本周一下午4時，兩批書店職員拉客時起爭執，其間有人出言恐嚇：「信唔信我打你！」警方到場截停10人，當中包括9名少年男女，其後以涉嫌刑事恐嚇及遊蕩拘捕各人。<br />\n據稱，葵涌廣場有多間書店，每年暑假賣二手教科書盈利可觀，負責拉客的青少年可抽佣10%，有指7月旺季時每日收入逾千元，因此常因爭生意發生糾紛。"},{"pid":"11e29569cd4d3ee43d2a1ee04149a0edce307912","tid":747597,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T13:25:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20170816/large/1502891824_fc0d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170816%2Flarge%2F1502891824_fc0d.jpg&h=514e637e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"88474e2d466c2b99062650102d485b7ae38c4967","tid":747597,"uid":54373,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T13:28:10.000Z","msg":"林雪: 我買書ja喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/QYRfjj68fes\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FQYRfjj68fes&d=e18W%2Be2xcDlblVKEWQ0FAAKEmdudW1rq3V1Y15kzxIU%3D&h=8238fb2d\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/QYRfjj68fes</a>"},{"pid":"9d310387d02450fb20e91df89c074aad62a80356","tid":747597,"uid":96486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"11e29569cd4d3ee43d2a1ee04149a0edce307912","tid":747597,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T13:25:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20170816/large/1502891824_fc0d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170816%2Flarge%2F1502891824_fc0d.jpg&h=514e637e&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T13:47:41.000Z","msg":"正呀，夠哂青春"},{"pid":"354daa60aa819c909c1b96b62ba461ef4605dcd7","tid":747597,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T14:01:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97e6ba03b90c75ebb99b07648c7c7364cb2e8734","tid":747597,"uid":44333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T14:09:23.000Z","msg":"姐姐我想模你"},{"pid":"a724bfce7d2cee284c92ef0115ac4ee80172acc9","tid":747597,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T04:21:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}